$wpdb->query("INSERT INTO `hc_cards` (`id`,`created_at`,`updated_at`,`deck`,`name`,`background_image`,`background_color`,`border_color`,`text_color`,`illustration`,`reference`,`reference2`,`gender`,`ext_id`,`year`,`maintype`,`continent`,`is_coastal`,`nationality`,`religion`,`climate`,`ethnicity`,`strength`,`defense`,`carry_capacity`,`when_to_play`,`summary`,`abilities`) VALUES  (1,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-09 02:45:06','A','Frederick Douglass','','white','none','black','','US Civil War',' ','male','AC4101','1818-1895',2,0,0,0,0,0,0,60,0,'1','C','Taking the surname \"Douglass\" after gaining his freedom, he became a spokesman for abolitionist societies and the US Constitution\'s 3/5 clause. For 17 years, he published and managed a newspaper supporting black freedom. During the Civil War, he used his fame to recruit free African Americans into the Union Army, contributing to its  victory.   ','Douglass inspires all your black Characters. For every black Character in your Civilization, increase his Land\'s Defense by 200.'),(2,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-10 21:38:51','A','Susan B. Anthony','','white','none','black','','Women\'s Rights',' ','female','AC4102','1820-1906',2,0,0,0,0,0,95,40,0,'1','I','Anthony, along with Fredrick Douglass and Elizabeth Cady Stanton, was an icon of the suffrage movement. For 15years, her teaching career had limited her time for activism, so she quit her job to fight for civil rights and to co-found  a women’s rights journal. Anthony and Stanton helped write the 19th constitutional amendment.','Anthony adds strength to female Characters. For every woman in your Civilization, increase your Morale by 200.'),(3,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:22:49','A','English Army','','white','none','black','','Middle Ages',' ','male','AR4101','1066 - 1604',33,0,0,0,0,0,0,3000,0,'1','C','The dawn of the English Army began when William the Conqueror defeated the Celts on the Isle of Britton in 1066.  The English Army and its  legendary longbows were feared in Europe through the end of the Hundred Years’ War.  Later, it  became known as the British Army when King James I formed Great Britain in 1604.','The English Army increases his Land’s Strength by 300 if it fights  on behalf of the United Kingdom or an English Leader.'),(4,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Mongolian Army (Cover)','0','white','none','black','0','Central Asian Wars',' ','male','AR4102','1206BC - 1368AD',33,0,0,0,0,0,0,4000,0,'1','H','Genghis Khan unified all Mongolian territories into the Mongol Empire in 1206 AD and combined the territorial warriors into one army. This army conquered all of Asia, the Middle East, and parts of Eastern Europe. Considered the first modern military system, it  used foreign weapons and, to a small extent, warships. ','The Mongolian Army wins its  first attack on any Land, beating any other card with the same type of ability.'),(5,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Steel Workers','0','white','none','black','0','Industrial Revolution',' ','male','AR4103','June 30, 1892',33,0,0,0,0,0,0,1500,0,'1','C','In 1892, Pennsylvania steel workers became enraged when Andrew Carnegie failed to give them a promised wage increase. In a standoff known as the Homestead Strike, the workers  revolted and blocked efforts to bring in scab workers to resume production. The US military stepped in when the uprising turned violent and a battle ensued. ','CHOICE: With every battle you win, increase this card\'s Attack or Defense by 500.'),(6,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-08 16:37:49','A','Viet Minh Guerrillas','','white','none','black','','Vietnam War',' ','male','AR4104','1941-1975',33,0,0,0,80,0,95,2000,0,'1','C','Trained and led by Ho Chi Minh\\\'s communists in China, their  ultimate goal was to drive out Western rule from Asia. During WWII, the forces conducted guerrilla operations against the Japanese invaders in Vietnam . When Vietnam split in 1954, the North marched on the South, initiating the Vietnam War.','If the Viet Minh fight in Asia, increase this card\'s Attack Strength by 1,000.'),(7,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-08 16:40:26','A','Leonardo da Vinci','','white','none','black','','The Renaissance',' ','male','AI4101','1452 - 1519',3,0,0,0,81,0,91,80,0,'1','C','Da Vinci was a \\\"Renaissance polymath\\\": a writer, painter, sculptor, architect, musician, scientist, mathematician, engineer, inventor, anatomist, geologist, botanist, and cartographer. Educated from birth by other famous artists, he is considered one of the greatest minds of all time.','You may use all your opponents’ Technology cards until Leonardo is discarded.'),(8,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-08 16:41:37','A','Mary Elizabeth Bowser','','white','none','black','','US Civil War','Jefferson Davis','female','SY4101','1839-1865',31,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','C','As a well-educated former slave, , Bowser worked as a spy in the Jefferson Davis household during the Civil War. Her education and supposedly photographic memory helped her recognize and relay information to the Union Army. When a leak was suspected, Bowser fled--after she set fire to the Davis home. ','Bowser allows you to look at one opponents\' hand per turn. Through reconnaissance,   increase your Land’s Strength by 400.'),(9,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-08 16:42:19','A','Jesse Owens','','white','none','black','','Olympics','Adolph Hitler','male','AT4101','1895-1948',6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','I','Jesse Owens, the grandson of a slave, achieved something no Olympian before him had ever accomplished. At the 1936 Berlin Olympic Games, he earned four gold medals. His outstanding performance discredited Adolph Hitler\\\'s heinous claims about racial superiority. His long-jump world record stood for 25 years.','Jesse Owens\' inspires your people. Increase your Morale by 200.'),(10,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-11 00:23:01','A','C.S. Lewis','','white','none','black','','World War I',' ','male','AU4101','1898 - 1963',7,0,0,0,0,0,0,200,0,'1','I','Irish-born Lewis dreamed up many vivid imaginary worlds as a child. Early into his university studies, Lewis left Christianity for atheism. WWI service and further studies saw him return to his Christian faith and to a quest for truth. His faith can be found in many of his writings including his Narnia series.','Increase your Morale by 200. For each Christian Leader in your Civilization, increase your Morale by an additional 100.'),(11,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Homer','0','white','none','black','0','The Greek Era',' ','male','AU4102','8th century BC',7,0,0,0,0,0,0,100,0,'1','I','Famous for The Odyssey and The Iliad, Homer\'s personal history is largely unknown. Some scholars say he was Greek, others Babylonian. Some say his epics were autobiographical; others mention his travels as a wandering minstrel. Regardless, Homer\'s influence on early European literature is unquestionable.','INTERRUPT: Sneak into one of your opponents’ Lands  and kill any one Character card with 100 or fewer Attack.'),(12,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-07-10 21:21:01','A','Madam CJ Walker','','white','none','black','','Civil Rights',' ','female','BU4101','1867-1919',8,0,0,0,0,0,0,40,0,'1','C','Born Sarah Breedlove, she created a specialized line of hair-care products for African American hair. She was the first female African American self-made millionaire. While seeking a treatment for her own hair loss, she developed the “Walker system.” From then on she was known as Madam CJ Walker.','Madam Walker\'s products are uplifting. For every black woman played, until Walker is discarded , increase your Morale by 100.'),(13,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:20:55','A','Charlemagne','','white','none','black','','The Middle Ages',' ','male','CO4101','742 - 814',9,0,0,0,0,0,0,800,0,'1','C','Charlemagne, the 8th century King of the Franks, was honored by Rome after assuming the Iron Crown of Italy. While Charlemagne was battling Spain, the Romans threatened Pope Leo III. Charlemagne returned to defend Leo and was crowned the first Holy Roman Emperor. The Catholic Church still hails him as the first Champion of Christianity.','CHOICE: If battling in Europe, your Attack OR Defense increases by an additional 500.'),(14,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:22:35','A','Eric Bloodaxe','','white','none','black','','The Viking Era',' ','male','CO4102','885 - 954',9,0,0,0,0,0,0,800,0,'1','C','Eric Bloodaxe was a greatly feared 10th century king of Western Norway. Ousted from the throne by his more popular half-brother, he moved to the British Isles, raided Scotland and Ireland, and established himself as ruler of the Viking Kingdom of Northumbria until his death in 954 AD. His sons later took back Norway.  His name continued to spread fear posthumously.','During every attack, your opponent\'s Defense decreases by 500 until the end of that round.'),(15,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:24:23','A','Timur the Lame\'','','white','none','black','','Central Asian Wars',' ','male','CO4103','1336-1405',9,0,0,0,0,0,0,1500,0,'1','C','Also known as Tamerlane, son of a minor Turk chieftain, he was a feared mercenary. His army of 90,000 men killed around 19 million people. He seized central Asia, Russia, Persia, India, Syria, Turkey, and Egypt. Lack of foresight, by not building governmental order, led to his empire\'s demise after his death.','When Timur attacks in Asia or Africa, add an additional 1,000 Attack.'),(16,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:25:49','A','Alaska','','white','none','black','','North America','Constitutional Republic','male','CT4101',' ',0,79,1,0,79,0,96,0,0,'1','C','Population (US):  319M; Land (US): 9,826,675 km2Capital (US): Washington, DC; Eligible for Military (US): 145M                   Indigenous people occupied Alaska for thousands of years before the first European settlements. In 1867, the US purchased Alaska, larger than TX, CA, and MT combined, from Russia for $7.2M. ','With any Native American Army in Alaska, increase your Strength by 1,000.'),(17,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Colombia','0','white','none','black','0','South America','Republic','male','CT4102',' ',0,83,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','C','Population: 47,425,437; Land: 1,141,748 km2Capital: Bogotá; Eligible for Military: 23,420,272 Santa María la Antigua del Darién was the first city established in the Americas by the conquistadors. Colombia has seen intense political feuding between liberals and conservatives since 1946. ',' '),(18,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Democratic Republic of the Congo','0','white','none','black','0','Africa','Republic','male','CT4103',' ',0,82,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','C','Population: 77,433,744; Land: 2,344,858 km2Capital: Kinshasa; Eligible for Military: 15,980,106  The Democratic Republic of the Congo became free in 1877, then became a Belgian colony in 1908, and became independent again in 1960. Military coups and wars have made Congo militarily strong in the region. ','When a rebel Army sets up camp in Congo, add 500 Strength.'),(19,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Germany','0','white','none','black','0','Europe','Federal Republic','male','CT4104',' ',0,81,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','C','Population: 80,585,700; Land: 357,168 km2Capital: Berlin; Eligible for Military: 36,417,842 Germany is currently the economic titan of Europe. Following World War II, Germany was divided into communist East Germany and democratic West Germany. This division ended in 1989 with the fall of the Berlin Wall.  ','Your Land\'s Strength increases by 500 unless a World War card is played in battle.'),(20,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Saudi Arabia','0','white','none','black','0','Africa/Asia','Monarchy','male','CT4105',' ',0,80,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','C','Population: 27,345,986; Land: 2,149,690 km2Capital: Riyadh; Eligible for Military: 15,246,507 Saudi Arabia has long been marred by tribal conflict. In 1902, Abd al Aziz began peace efforts through unification but has long been a target of attacks due to oil resources and Western cooperation. ','If an Asian, European, or African Land is threatened with imminent takeover, all Character and Army cards may be moved to this Land. Land rules apply.'),(21,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Tonga','0','white','none','black','0','South Pacific','Constitutional Monarchy','male','CT4106',' ',0,85,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','I','Population:  106,440; Land: 747 km2Capital: Nuku\'alofa; Eligible for Military: 48,501 Made up of 176 islands, Tonga is an indigenously governed nation and monarchy in the Pacific. Known as the “Friendly Islands” because of the warm welcome extended to Captain Cook, it first became a unified kingdom in 1845.  In 1970, Tonga joined the Commonwealth of Nations. ','Enjoying the beauty of the islands increases your Morale by 300 points.'),(22,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:27:54','A','U.S. Constitution','','white','none','black','','American Revolution','Declaration of Independence','male','DO4101','September 17, 1787',41,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','C','Colonial Representatives from the 13 colonies met in the Pennsylvania State House in May 1787 to revise the Articles of Confederation. Due to lack of attendance and concerns about representation and what was best for the new United States, an agreement wasn\'t finalized and adopted until Sept. 17, 1787.','Increase your Morale by 400 when played. Increase your Civilization\'s Defense by 300.'),(23,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Adam Smith','0','white','none','black','0','Economics',' ','male','EC4101','1723-1790',11,0,0,0,0,0,0,70,0,'1','I','Scottish-born Smith studied to be a political economist and became a professor of logic and of moral philosophy at Glasgow University. His two iconic books were The Theory of Moral Sentiments, written in 1759, and The Wealth of Nations, written in 1776. .  Smith laid the intellectual framework for the free market we enjoy today.','You can exchange any one card from your opponent\'s hand with a card in your own. Both parties must agree on the exchange.'),(24,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Charlie Chaplin','0','white','none','black','0','Classical Cinema',' ','male','EN4101','1889 - 1977',10,0,0,0,0,0,0,80,0,'1','C','Chaplin, a stage actor at the age of 5, toured the US as a member of a traveling performing troupe. His first job in the US was with the Keystone Film Company for $125 per week. He went on to earn over $1 million per year. He is still an icon of comedic silent films, earning the nickname \"The Little Tramp.\"','Increase your Morale by 100 every turn until Chaplin is discarded or until your Morale reaches 1,500 points.'),(25,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Dark Ages','0','white','none','black','0','The Dark Ages','Renaissance','male','EV4101','5th to 10th Centuries',36,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','I','The Dark Ages is mostly recognized as the time between the end of the Western Roman Empire and the beginning of the Italian Renaissance. This period gets its name from the western European decline in historical record-keeping, the waning of Latin literacy and cultural achievements, and the demographic deterioration in Europe experienced during this time.  ','CHOICE: One opponent must discard all Knowledge and Technology cards in play.'),(26,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','','A','Gold Rush','0','white','none','black','0','The Wild West','Yukon, Canada','male','EV4102','1848 - 1905',36,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','I','In 1848, the discovery of gold in California inspired thousands from eastern states to move west, dreaming of striking it rich. Prospectors ranged from California to Alaska and the Yukon. Hundreds lost everything, including their lives. The cost of supplies crushed many dreams in the early stages.','Add a new Land to your civilization.'),(27,'2020-07-08 14:13:46','2020-08-06 02:29:21','A','American Slavery','','white','none','black','','US Civil War','Hyram Rhodes Revels','male','EV4103','8000 BC',36,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'1','I','Early in American history, African people were brought to the continent as slaves. Chinese and European immigrants who could not pay for the journey came to America as indentured